        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/rescuers-evacuate-wounded-person-russian-missile-strike-sumy-ukraine.png" alt="Rescuers and volunteers evacuate a wounded person from an apartment building damaged during a Russian missile strike amid Russia's attack on Ukraine in Sumy" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
